While vendoring {{bson-atomic.h}} into PHPC, I noticed that {{BSON_IF_MSVC}} is [sometimes redefined|https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-c-driver/blob/master/src/libbson/src/bson/bson-atomic.h#L81], and unlike other defs in that header it's not [undefined later|https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-c-driver/blob/master/src/libbson/src/bson/bson-atomic.h#L650]. It looks like this could possibly conflict with another definition of the macro in {{{}bson-compat.h{}}}
